Your API token for <%= @restaurant.name %>
============================================

An API access token has been created for your restaurant.

Token name: <%= @jwt_token.name %>
Expires: <%= @expires_at.strftime('%d %B %Y at %H:%M UTC') %>
Scopes: <%= @scopes.join(', ') %>

YOUR API TOKEN (shown once only)
---------------------------------
<%= @raw_jwt %>

Keep this token secure. Do not share it publicly or commit it to version control.

HOW TO USE YOUR TOKEN
----------------------
Include the token in the Authorization HTTP header for every API request:

  Authorization: Bearer <your-token>

Example:
  curl https://mellow.menu/api/v1/restaurants/<%= @restaurant.id %>/menus \
    -H "Authorization: Bearer <your-token>"

If you did not request this token or believe it was issued in error, please
contact hello@mellow.menu immediately.
